   Sharper Image's Loss Widens
</HL>
<DATE>
05/24/90
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), NO PAGE CITATION
</SO>
<CO>
   SHRP
</CO>
<IN>
EARNINGS (ERN)
