PETROLEUM (PET)
</IN>
<LP>
   DeKalb Energy Co. said it purchased an interest in 36
onshore oil and gas fields that it believes will increase its
proven U.S. reserves by more than 70%.
   The $130.2 million acquisition from Pittsburgh-based Royal
Producing Corp. Texas involves approximately 250 producing
wells, most of them located on the Texas Gulf Coast, and
